data.description: Only 1/2 mile from the Oriole Beach Boat ramp, this home is considered in the heart of Gulf Breeze and is close to all amenities that the city has to offer. This open and light turn-key home has been freshly painted and is move in ready.  As you enter, you will see vaulted ceilings in the living room with a pass through kitchen and a dining area with bay windows that reveal the backyard suitable for rest or play. Privacy fencing and mature foliage/trees provides a peaceful feeling. The covered porch area allows one to relax while watching children play in the backyard or to just enjoy the surrounding nature. The kitchen has ample cabinet storage, a lazy-susan corner cabinet, a flat-top stove, a side-by-side refrigerator (with ice and water in the door), and a brand new dishwasher. This home has the desirable split floor plan with the master bedroom (fit for a King bed) located on the left side of the home and the other two bedrooms on the right side. The master suite features a shower-tub combo, walk-in closet, and water closet. Each bedroom boasts crown molding and windows for plenty of natural light. Because of the vicinity to the boat ramp and being just 7 miles from Pensacola Beach, this home is perfect for someone wanting to live and enjoy the community or for an investor. For this price in GB, it is a must see.
